race.comment: HOPE'S ZONE (8) turned in a moderate run last time when eighth at this track over 352m behind PERKY PENNY (20.17) in a Grade 1/2. Scored at her previous run. Speedy runner who can find the front with a clear break from out wide. Should bounce back. MILO DAVIS (4) has shown good improvement at his last two starts, hitting the frame latest when 2nd at this track over 352m. Expected to be in the finish again. PERKY PENNY (3) comes into this as a quickest on the card winner last time at this track, scoring by a nose (19.53). Has good speed and aided by a low draw. Deserved serious consideration again. OUT OF AUSTRIAN (2) will have admirers after placing last time out.
